Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:47.54,0:01:49.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真得受不了了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:49.74,0:01:51.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想就这样死掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.84,0:01:57.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们…连死都不被允许
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:59.44,0:02:01.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想再忍受更多痛苦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:01.94,0:02:04.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少可以把所有的一切都忘掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.34,0:02:11.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第十六话 追忆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:29.34,0:02:30.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你醒了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.94,0:02:48.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是哪里？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.94,0:02:50.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在你的房间里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.84,0:02:55.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是谁？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.44,0:02:59.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Lumiere 你的搭档
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.74,0:03:01.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搭档？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.64,0:03:04.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Lumiere…然后什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.54,0:03:07.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有Lumiere而已啊 Eclair
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.14,0:03:09.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Eclair？ 那是我的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.94,0:03:13.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是你的名字 Eclair
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.94,0:03:25.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是…我？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.24,0:03:29.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这样年纪的女孩子可不能这么做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.84,0:03:31.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要碰我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.14,0:03:37.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Eclair…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.84,0:03:43.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种力量是什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.04,0:03:50.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Eclair…那就是我的名字吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.34,0:03:52.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.14,0:03:53.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Eclair…然后什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.44,0:03:55.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有Eclair而已啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.44,0:03:56.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别开玩笑了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.34,0:04:00.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么这种力量又是什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.04,0:04:06.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你的才能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.04,0:04:07.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.44,0:04:09.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗人 骗人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.54,0:04:11.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗人的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.24,0:04:22.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是谁？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.34,0:04:24.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什么人？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.14,0:04:26.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么我会…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.94,0:04:30.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我比任何人都了解你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.74,0:04:34.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,力量强 速度快 还很温柔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.04,0:04:37.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些事我会一点一点地告诉你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.04,0:04:39.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.74,0:04:43.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我绝对不会骗你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.04,0:04:48.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直相信你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.44,0:05:15.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.24,0:05:18.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒是你没问题了吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.24,0:05:25.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题吧 Eclair？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.04,0:05:27.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.74,0:05:30.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来我至少还记得如何沐浴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.94,0:05:34.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Eclair
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.34,0:05:37.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我的名字是男孩的名字…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.84,0:05:40.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但感觉好像在某个地方听过好多次了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.94,0:05:44.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把毛巾放这儿了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.54,0:05:46.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.84,0:05:49.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉好极了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.04,0:05:51.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.04,0:05:56.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之 得先解决你的穿着问题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.24,0:06:07.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些都是你的衣服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.54,0:06:18.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们还是先吃些东西吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.84,0:06:32.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女孩子要优雅些
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.04,0:06:37.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请稍等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.74,0:06:45.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你很喜欢吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.94,0:06:47.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 十分喜欢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.24,0:06:48.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你毕竟是个女孩子啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.64,0:06:52.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 既然是女孩子就要更优雅些
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.74,0:06:56.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,优雅…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.44,0:07:02.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你必须学很多东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.14,0:07:04.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了代替过去的记忆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.24,0:07:06.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,代替过去的记忆？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.14,0:07:08.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是奇怪的说法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.54,0:07:11.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 我说错了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.34,0:07:14.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该说为了使你恢复记忆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.84,0:07:18.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么不对吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.24,0:07:22.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没 你果然是我的搭档啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.74,0:07:25.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知为何我十分安心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.14,0:07:29.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢 很高兴听你这么说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.54,0:07:31.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个人是谁？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.04,0:07:34.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Eclipse
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.74,0:07:36.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是我们的所属机关
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.54,0:07:41.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,银河通商关税机构-GOTT总局的局长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.74,0:07:44.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是漂亮的人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.74,0:07:46.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你早晚会见到她的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.24,0:07:49.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个建筑物呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.74,0:07:51.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GOTT总局
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.84,0:07:55.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是兼管Aineias上一切事物的行政机关
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.54,0:07:58.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 接下来学习历史吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.64,0:08:07.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.04,0:08:08.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真的可以外出吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.94,0:08:23.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让你久等了
