Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.24,0:08:29.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,6:30 不过6点以后就开门了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.14,0:08:31.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.44,0:08:33.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们可以来这里吃早饭了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.84,0:08:36.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两位客人是第一次来本店吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.74,0:08:38.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是姐妹吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.44,0:08:39.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是表姐妹？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.44,0:08:42.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是姐妹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.24,0:08:46.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近我姐姐要开始在这附近独自生活了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.24,0:08:47.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请你多关照了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.24,0:08:51.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望你能经常来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.44,0:08:56.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是卡普里斯 是店里的看板娘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.04,0:08:58.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请多关照 我是Eclair
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.94,0:09:01.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个孩子是我妹妹Lumiere
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.44,0:09:04.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡普里斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.64,0:09:05.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.14,0:09:06.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请慢用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.24,0:09:13.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我做得没错吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.94,0:09:15.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,合格了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.14,0:09:18.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 你说的独自生活是？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.34,0:09:21.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你已经没问题了对吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.14,0:09:23.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过一阵子我会再来看你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.44,0:09:27.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让你久等了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.84,0:09:34.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了 来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.84,0:09:39.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Lumiere 进来进来 我去倒咖啡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.64,0:09:40.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用那么麻烦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.94,0:09:44.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么不适应的地方吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.24,0:09:46.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一点也没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.34,0:09:49.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我对于你给的训练表已经厌烦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.34,0:09:52.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些照片是什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.64,0:09:53.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.04,0:09:54.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋友…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.04,0:09:58.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你喜欢拍照吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.84,0:10:00.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.64,0:10:06.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是希望不会再忘记他们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.34,0:10:09.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样吗…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.14,0:10:20.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎… 她叫Donnerschlag啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.74,0:10:24.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请多关照 Donner
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.14,0:10:25.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是Eclair
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.14,0:10:37.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总觉得有似曾相识的感觉啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.64,0:10:52.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这支最适合我了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.14,0:10:55.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过缺少了些东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.54,0:11:03.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你的枪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.24,0:11:04.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.34,0:11:18.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎你们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.44,0:11:20.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Eclair、Lumiere
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.94,0:11:58.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是银河通商关税机构 GOTT所属ES成员
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.04,0:12:03.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Eclair和Lumiere的最新监视报告
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.34,0:12:06.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至于文件的时间标记
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.64,0:12:08.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在记录档案的不同层面上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.64,0:12:11.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准备了不可修改的一份
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.24,0:12:14.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不需要那样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.84,0:12:17.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是因为我相信你的人格
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.74,0:12:20.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才拜托你执行这个任务
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.34,0:12:22.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我的荣幸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.04,0:12:30.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以下摘录上次报告以后发生的主要事件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.94,0:12:33.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先应该是Faunus-Medeia危机
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.94,0:12:39.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了避免商业行星Faunus 和矿业行星Medeia之间发生冲突
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.14,0:12:42.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原本任务目的是签订谈判协定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.64,0:12:43.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过您也知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.84,0:12:49.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不如说解决操纵Faunus的两派贵族间的争执
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.94,0:12:52.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能比较妥当
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.94,0:12:56.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们让你在这一事件中经历了很多麻烦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.04,0:12:57.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.64,0:12:58.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请您别这么说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.74,0:13:02.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后是马克思事件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.54,0:13:09.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逮捕十名非法制造 贩卖重力控制物质Hi-G的贵族后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.34,0:13:14.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她们卷入了揭露Shopper这类犯罪组织的事件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.74,0:13:18.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及处理贵族子女失踪事件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.84,0:13:25.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Rosenfelt家族继承者事件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.04,0:13:29.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那个时候 我们可以看出金融管理局的敌对态度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.94,0:13:35.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而结果是GOTT赢得贸易上的有利因素
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.24,0:13:36.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.44,0:13:39.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后是非法产品Geo-Sorter炸弹事件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.64,0:13:42.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她们也卷入那起事件了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.54,0:13:43.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.14,0:13:46.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那件事大概是贵族们操纵的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.94,0:13:50.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过一个星球 被彻底毁灭了的事实是无法隐藏的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.84,0:13:56.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是一件众所周知的事 不过知道真相的人大概不多吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.54,0:14:00.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随后是行星Dardanos
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.24,0:14:03.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是一个试验区吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.04,0:14:04.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,试验区？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.14,0:14:07.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么你这样想？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.04,0:14:10.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诱导民众意识的试验
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.84,0:14:15.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我猜那是支配银河系的贵族们干的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.64,0:14:18.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是全体贵族的意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.24,0:14:22.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是统治Dardanos的人的愚蠢行为造成的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.24,0:14:26.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当局已经让他们得到了应有的惩罚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.24,0:14:31.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过连Dardanos事件也卷入
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.44,0:14:36.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该说是因果报应？ 我感觉到有某种宿命的存在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.74,0:14:40.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事情会是GOTT总局局长坚持的那样吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.44,0:14:41.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.74,0:14:44.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个我也不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.14,0:14:48.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少行星Aure事件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.34,0:14:50.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是她坚持的那样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.24,0:14:52.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秘密花园吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.24,0:14:54.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也很吃惊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.94,0:15:01.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当中央委员会成员提到 Eclair这个名字时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.84,0:15:05.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么这件事的报告…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.14,0:15:06.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不必说了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.14,0:15:09.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经知道了详细的情况
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.74,0:15:11.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是很悲哀啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.34,0:15:12.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.04,0:15:16.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消除命令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.64,0:15:19.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说得到了死刑命令 两人开始逃亡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.74,0:15:25.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她们设法躲过了 GOTT SO成员和ES成员的追击
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.84,0:15:32.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是机器人护卫 和专用高速巡洋舰的AI被控制了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.04,0:15:33.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被强迫和她们战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.14,0:15:40.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当时我没有跟着她们 所以不知道详情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.14,0:15:42.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果很明显
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.14,0:15:45.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,造成她们两个攻击GOTT总部的事件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.84,0:15:49.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然有三对ES成员阻止她们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.64,0:15:54.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GOTT毁灭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.34,0:16:04.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关于每个事件的详细情报 我都整理在文件里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.14,0:16:21.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.74,0:16:26.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.64,0:16:28.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不必客气
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.44,0:16:39.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么现在Aineias的情况如何？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.24,0:16:44.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GOTT目前正在重建
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.24,0:16:47.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,局长Eclipse死亡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.84,0:16:52.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暂时从ES成员中选出了一个代理局长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.34,0:16:56.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,代理局长？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.64,0:16:57.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.14,0:17:03.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽说是选出 实际上是行星联盟评议会指明的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.34,0:17:07.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行星联盟评议会的人吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.84,0:17:10.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么是谁？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.34,0:17:12.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被选上的是谁？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.04,0:17:15.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是Eclair
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.04,0:17:19.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说她是个自主的新局长也没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.24,0:17:24.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Eclair…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.34,0:17:30.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.34,0:17:34.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她用倒塌在总部大楼旁的附属建筑物 作为临时办公室
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.74,0:17:37.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并且已经开始活动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.64,0:17:39.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.34,0:17:42.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反应真的很快呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.94,0:17:48.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她们还组织了十二名新的ES成员
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:49.54,0:17:52.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,试图增强自主的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.44,0:17:54.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽说如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.84,0:17:57.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实是改编以前全部的ES成员
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.74,0:18:07.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在Atlas级宇宙船建造即将完成的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.24,0:18:08.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是件棘手的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:14.34,0:18:18.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是你派遣我们的原因吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.74,0:18:20.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是唯一的原因
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.54,0:18:25.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请继续监视她们的动静
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.74,0:18:30.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遵命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.74,0:18:35.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告辞了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:41.64,0:18:44.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是个比我想象的还要笨的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.74,0:18:48.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过我也没资格评论别人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.14,0:18:56.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,资料传输 使用G5级秘密线路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.84,0:19:20.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很久不见了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:21.14,0:19:24.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很抱歉让你干这样的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:24.94,0:19:27.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请别说见外的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.64,0:19:30.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们从中学时代起就是朋友了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.54,0:19:33.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:34.14,0:19:37.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看上去GOTT遇到大麻烦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.84,0:19:38.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:38.94,0:19:40.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且很可疑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.74,0:19:44.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说是行星联盟评议会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.04,0:19:46.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实是中央委员会的别名罢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.94,0:19:49.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过如果他们参与的话…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:50.34,0:19:52.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我早有心理准备了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.74,0:19:54.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.74,0:19:57.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我保证我不再参与此事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.74,0:20:01.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是你为什么不自己调查呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.64,0:20:05.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能看到你的后背吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.64,0:20:07.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧
